You can change the ###'s to whatever NPC ID that you want
Save and close class5.java.

[i]Step 2:[/i] Now download these models (the link is 100% by me, no viruses): http://www.mediafire.com/?zmew0cowbd9

Add those models to your models folder. Then get on your client and run your server and log on and type:

add model 9012
add model 9016
add model 9018
add model 10055

If you haven't done a model adding tut, I will post one later, if you have, you've just added the models to your client successfully.

[i]Step 3:[/i] Log off and close your client and compile it. Then log on and spawn the NPC's. They should successfully appear! You've just added 4 summoning NPC's!

